# Leave empty for local dev (Vite proxies /api and /socket.io to localhost:5004).
# In production set BOTH to your deployed chat backend URL (a persistent host
# like Render or Railway — NOT Vercel serverless, which can't hold websockets):
#   VITE_API_URL=https://your-chat-backend.onrender.com
#   VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://your-chat-backend.onrender.com
VITE_API_URL=
VITE_SOCKET_URL=
